column5: Going up to Gullrock August Week 1 and looking for the best quality/quantity leeches on the way up or in Red Lake. We were not "impressed" with the ones we reserved in a reputable shop in Ear Falls last year...who's got the scoop? Thanks, Craig
Try D&E Minnows in Ear Falls, I didn't buy leeches from them but it was one of the best places to buy minnows I have ever been to.http://www.deminnows.ca/
Anyone else have an opinion? Craig
